        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Addition of the selected points (ask the patient):</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"226\" /><col width=\"116\" /><col width=\"108\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Question</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Correct</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Incorrect</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Age</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Time (to the nearest hour)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Give the patient the following address for recall at end of test: &ldquo;42 West Street&rdquo; (have patient repeat to ensure it has been heard correctly)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Current year</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Patient&rsquo;s home address</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">What jobs do these people do? (show the patient two pictures: a postman and a cook)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Date of birth</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Year World War I started</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Current president (use setting-specific equivalent, e.g. &ldquo;monarch&rdquo; in the UK)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Count backwards from 20 to 1</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Ask to recall address given earlier (i.e., 42 West Street)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1 point</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0 points</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>From&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19790838\" target=\"_blank\">Abbreviated Mental Test Score 1993</a>.</p>\n</div>",
        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"138\" /><col width=\"228\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>AMT-10 Score</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Severity of delirium</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0-3</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Severe cognitive impairment</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">4-6</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Moderate cognitive impairment</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&gt;6</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">No delirium</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e04a9c5f-7fff-7926-29bf-ed467c47f413\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e04a9c5f-7fff-7926-29bf-ed467c47f413\">From <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19790838\" target=\"_blank\">Abbreviated Mental Test Score 1993</a>.</p>\n<p>Note:&nbsp;Some authors (e.g.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/psyg.12276\" target=\"_blank\">Foroughan 2017</a>) suggest a cutoff of 7 for cognitive impairment.</p>",
